{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_zst","exhibition_name":"展览二区","location":"508,745","name":"竹石图","size":"清 纵157cm，横78cm","like":4,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=89","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_zst","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"郑板桥，1693至1765，原名郑燮，字克柔，号理庵，又号板桥，人称板桥先生，扬州八怪之 一，江苏兴化人，祖籍苏州。小时候聪颖好学，尤爱字画，有诗、书、画“三绝”之誉，擅长画兰、竹、石、松、菊等，而以兰竹最为著名。《竹石图》是郑板桥62岁时画的庭院之竹，以白描笔意为主，中锋勾勒，用笔致瘦硬的长折带皴勾出坚硬挺削的石质，极尽变化，神韵具足。石前有两三枝劲拔挺秀的新篁修竹，有呼有应。整个画面，简约明快，竹清石秀，气势俊迈，风神肃散，有傲然挺立、不可一世之概。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/xvJoBt9n8_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/xvJoBt9n81_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/xvJoBt9n82_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/xvJoBt9n83_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/xvJoBt9n84_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/nIruTkd2e5.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}